description.narrative: Improved sanitation and hygiene behaviours and sector stakeholders have enhanced capacity to provide access to safe and sustainable sanitation and hygiene facilities in homes and institutions, which contributes to Disaster Risk Reduction, Environmental Sustainability, Sanitation, Sanitation (Covid).
